data.description: SELLER OFFERING UP TO $10K TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY DOWN** Large RV parking and covered boat port with hard wired owned security system with 8 cameras to protect all your toys!  Extra large remodeled Main bedroom with glorious Walk In Closet and french doors that lead out to the backyard deck with gas firepit and 8 person spa with ozonator conveys. Remodeled main bath with rain shower and spa tub.  Ceramic tile throughout, Corian counters, upgraded raised panel cabinets, gas burning brick fireplace, and a large laundry room.  Owned Solar over New Roof!  Gas stove, dryer, heat, and new hot water heater.  Owned reverse osmosis water softener.
